                "title": "Rastros de Qilin"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Ataque Normal</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191)\">Causa 2 pontos de </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Dano Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191)\">, causa 2 pontos de </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dano Perfurante</span><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191)\"> a todos os Personagens Inativos do oponente.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/16791688/c369b96fc6417e8fc2bb607e37297ad4_7337315945376753274.png",
